title: Episode 49: Guests Lisa Vischer & Amanda Jethani
description: Christian takes over the show!  Acting on a listener suggestion, she invites Skye's wife Amanda and Phil's wife Lisa to join her and dish on their husbands.  Phil's and Skye's ears are burning!
